abstract: Today I am free of the person I was, in order to be the person I so desperately needed to be.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Jacey Hoffman

abstract: I tried to fit in, tried to be the girl everyone said I was, and it worked, for a while.  But not before I slipped into a deep depression that took me years to crawl out of.
